====================
+++ Installation +++
====================

Clone:
    git clone git://github.com/rstratton/.vim.git ~/.vim

Create symlinks:

    ln -s ~/.vim/vimrc ~/.vimrc
    ln -s ~/.vim/gvimrc ~/.gvimrc

Switch to the `~/.vim` directory, and fetch submodules:

    cd ~/.vim
    git submodule init
    git submodule update



==============================
+++ Submodule Installation +++
==============================

cd ~/.vim
mkdir ~/.vim/bundle
git submodule add http://github.com/<github_acct>/<plugin>.git bundle/<plugin_name>
git add .
git commit -m "Install <plugin> as a submodule."
